===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 63 people, 27 households, and 21 families residing in the city. The median age was 37.5 years, with 28.6% of residents under the age of 18 and 12.7% of residents 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females there were 110.0 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 114.3 males.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A30540&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A30540&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A30540&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

The [[population density]] was 998.1 inhabitants per square mile (385.4/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 31 housing units at an average density of 491.1 per square mile (189.6/km<sup>2</sup>), of which 12.9% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%. All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DP"/><ref name="Census2020PL"/><ref name="Census2020DHC"/>

Of the 27 households, 37.0% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 33.3% were [[Marriage|married couples]] living together, 11.1% were cohabitating couples, 22.2% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present, and 33.3% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present. About 22.2% were non-families. About 11.1% of all households were made up of individuals, and 3.7% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

30.2% of residents were under the age of 20; 4.8% were between the ages of 20 and 24; 25.4% were from 25 to 44; and 27.0% were from 45 to 64. The gender makeup of the city was 52.4% male and 47.6% female.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

